jointLklDM.lklTerm014: FermiTables2016Lkl 0   logJ=18.8  DlogJ=0.19  inputfile=like_ursa_minor.txt
jointLklDM.lklTerm015: FermiTables2016Lkl 0   logJ=19.1  DlogJ=0.31  inputfile=like_willman_1.txt